<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Reseñas Google · Javier Estevez Quiropractico</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

  :root {
    --crema:   #faf7f2;
    --petroleo:#1D4E5F;
    --oro:     #c9a84c;
    --oro-light: #e8c96a;
    --ambar:   #7A5C2E;
    --blanco:  #ffffff;
    --texto:   #2a2a2a;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--crema);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--crema);
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(29,78,95,0.15), 0 2px 8px rgba(29,78,95,0.08);
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    background: var(--petroleo);
    padding: 32px 28px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px;
    left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 24px;
    background: var(--crema);
    border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0;
  }
  .header .brand {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--oro);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--blanco);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .header .subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* STARS */
  .stars {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin: 24px 0 8px;
  }
  .star {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--oro);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(201,168,76,0.5));
    animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .star:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .star:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; font-size: 34px; }
  .star:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .star:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  @keyframes glow {
    from { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(201,168,76,0.3)); }
    to   { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(201,168,76,0.8)); }
  }

  /* BODY */
  .body {
    padding: 8px 28px 28px;
  }

  .tagline {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--petroleo);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding: 0 8px;
  }
  .tagline strong {
    color: var(--ambar);
  }

  /* QR CONTAINER */
  .qr-wrap {
    background: var(--blanco);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    width: fit-content;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(29,78,95,0.12);
    border: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
    position: relative;
  }
  .qr-wrap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -4px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--oro) 0%, transparent 50%, var(--oro) 100%);
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .qr-wrap img {
    display: block;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .qr-caption {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ambar);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  /* SOCIAL PROOF */
  .social-proof {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--petroleo) 0%, #163d4d 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .social-proof p {
    color: var(--blanco);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .social-proof strong {
    color: var(--oro-light);
  }

  /* CTA BUTTON */
  .cta-btn {
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--oro) 0%, #b8922a 100%);
    color: var(--blanco);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(201,168,76,0.35);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
  }
  .cta-btn .icon { margin-right: 8px; font-size: 18px; }

  /* COPY BUTTON */
  .copy-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(29,78,95,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(29,78,95,0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .copy-url {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ambar);
    font-family: monospace;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .copy-btn {
    background: var(--petroleo);
    color: var(--blanco);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .copy-btn:hover { background: #163d4d; }
  .copy-btn.copied { background: #4A7C59; }

  /* INSTAGRAM SECTION */
  .instagram-section {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(29,78,95,0.1);
    padding-top: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .instagram-section p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ambar);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .ig-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #833ab4, #fd1d1d, #fcb045);
    color: var(--blanco);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    background: var(--petroleo);
    padding: 14px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .footer .fixmade {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--oro);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .footer .tagline-footer {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="body">

    <!-- STARS -->
    <div class="stars">
      <span class="star">★</span>
      <span class="star">★</span>
      <span class="star">★</span>
      <span class="star">★</span>
      <span class="star">★</span>
    </div>

    <!-- TAGLINE -->
    <p class="tagline">
      ¿Te sentiste mejor después del ajuste?<br>
      <strong>Tu testimonio ayuda a que otros vecinos<br>de San Martín encuentren el alivio que sentís vos.</strong>
    </p>

    <!-- QR -->
    <div class="qr-wrap">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="QR para dejar reseña en Google Maps">
      <div class="qr-caption">Escanear para calificar</div>
    </div>

    <!-- SOCIAL PROOF -->
    <div class="social-proof">
      <p>Más de <strong>100 vecinos de San Martín</strong> ya recuperaron su movilidad con nosotros.<br>
      Tu reseña es nuestro mejor agradecimiento. 🙌</p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA BUTTON -->
    <a href="https://g.page/r/Ca96yZ-I52_EEBM/review" class="cta-btn" target="_blank">
      <span class="icon">⭐</span> Dejar mi reseña en Google Maps
    </a>

    <!-- COPY PARA WHATSAPP -->
    <div class="copy-wrap">
      <span class="copy-url">https://g.page/r/Ca96yZ-I52_EEBM/review</span>
      <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyLink(this)">Copiar</button>
    </div>

    <!-- INSTAGRAM -->
    <div class="instagram-section">
      <p>También nos encontrás en</p>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/javierquiropraxia/" class="ig-btn" target="_blank">📷 Instagram · @javierquiropraxia</a>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<script>
function copyLink(btn) {
  navigator.clipboard.writeText('https://g.page/r/Ca96yZ-I52_EEBM/review').then(() => {
    btn.textContent = '¡Copiado!';
    btn.classList.add('copied');
    setTimeout(() => {
      btn.textContent = 'Copiar';
      btn.classList.remove('copied');
    }, 2000);
  });
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
